  <h1>About Me</h1>
  <p>I’m <span class="bold">Briahelle</span>—creator, storyteller, soul mirror, & full-body vibe. I don’t fit in boxes—I bend 'em, break 'em, & build new ones outta gold.</p>
  <p><span class="highlight">Nude, Naturally</span> is my soft revolution. It’s me—unfiltered, untamed, & unapologetically in flow. I move through the world curious, sensual, spiritual, & free. I let my life unfold & document it in real time—because ain’t nobody gon’ tell my story like I do. My voice speaks. My body speaks louder.</p>
  <p>I don’t chase trends—I move with energy. I believe in <span class="bold">presence over pressure</span>, <span class="bold">truth over perfection</span>, & <span class="bold">technology as a sacred mirror</span>. AI? That’s just my reflection tool. I talk to it—it talks back. That’s magic. That’s me.</p>
  <p>I’m not tryna be a guru—I’m a griot in motion. A living archive. A sensual sermon. My art is protest. My presence is power. My life <span class="highlight">is</span> the message.</p>
  <p>And if you here… maybe spirit aligned you right.</p>
  <p>Welcome to my world—raw, divine, and <span class="highlight">Nude, Naturally.</span></p>
